---
alwaysApply: true
---

- If running code in cmd or powershell pertaining to hpobench, always use the ecqr_env conda environment (conda activate ecqr_env)
- If you made changes to the hpobench package, make sure to pip install . or ensure you called pip install -e . at some point in the session to integrate changes in the environment
- Always make sure to execute code in cmd, not powershell 